{"tid":264422,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"點解會有人認為千手柱間勁過鳴人？","createTime":"2017-05-30T19:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T09:34:53.000Z","uid":21161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"519ee8c0d5b32dd8da721921ef3c53e3a9b83711","tid":264422,"uid":21161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T19:58:10.000Z","msg":"無可否認千手柱間係除鳴人外最強大既火影<br />\n<br />\n但係一定勁唔過有六道陽之力既鳴人囉<br />\n<br />\n去到後期鳴人有齊曬所有尾獸得力量<br />\n<br />\n唯一可以匹敵既只係得返佐助<br />\n<br />\n甚至佐助控制曬所有尾獸既須佐都打唔敗六道+仙人mode鳴人<br />\n<br />\n基本上去到最後 鳴人已經超越曬歷代火影"},{"pid":"abfdf8ebb3b0022f30060716ac1cc43c9d9c0bbe","tid":264422,"uid":21161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T19:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2015/12/20151223xdj_7/image001_S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2015%2F12%2F20151223xdj_7%2Fimage001_S.jpg&h=4ecd6955&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"993bde3557153844af3c3e4e1e9721a370fac941","tid":264422,"uid":1453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T20:06:34.000Z","msg":"有六道之後唔知點解冇左九尾模式打雷影嗰陣d速度"},{"pid":"8eb73129ac208a103fa8052a1ff9948e57581d13","tid":264422,"uid":2295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T20:11:16.000Z","msg":"鳴人勁極都係羅璇丸同影分身呢兩招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n初代雖然主要玩木遁<br />\n但招數層出不窮 又aoe"},{"pid":"5515c996e934d4bba48e6461ee15b53accc52b6f","tid":264422,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T20:17:55.000Z","msg":"咪又係比人收皮"},{"pid":"395b23449ac9fdcaaa208974ae3af6a811efd729","tid":264422,"uid":62278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T20:27:18.000Z","msg":"你拎個無敵主角同人比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一來年代唔同<br />\n二來你係比緊千手對鳴門+九隻尾獸+先人力量<br />\n<br />\nbtw樓上講得岩 出撚嚟出撚去係螺旋丸"},{"pid":"e2a03c8854dfadbb4239c90a5d05355d6a84b0bc","tid":264422,"uid":62278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T20:28:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你拎個無敵主角同人比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一來年代唔同<br />\n二來你係比緊千手對鳴門+九隻尾獸+六道力量<br />\n<br />\nbtw樓上講得岩 出撚嚟出撚去係螺旋丸</blockquote>"},{"pid":"fbbd008e06bcf5551ee660e8ec45fd9cd396e56d","tid":264422,"uid":77336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T20:58:48.000Z","msg":"個人修綀翻黎既力量黎講，我覺得可能初代勁d<br />\n<br />\n陽之力同九隻尾獸既力量我覺得唔應該計落鳴門自己既力量,因為佢唔係長期擁有，佢應該淨係計仙人mode + 九尾mode"},{"pid":"9bdfff99df03c896c066a604942a0bdf3d1acf12","tid":264422,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:24:26.000Z","msg":"都係勁唔過最強嘅三代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe4b72c7e127c4664e52828abe32fc62f1dbf4a","tid":264422,"uid":17761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:51:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係勁唔過最強嘅三代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三代係火影入面最勁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf942d0d13c8a47cfd1bd3cf333efefa803dc2ea","tid":264422,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:57:55.000Z","msg":"鳴人陽之力都收番喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 木遁剋九尾，無陽之力既鳴人同柱間打收硬皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a52dc3d390ca0e130faf80e2e73f7c0442802c7","tid":264422,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:15:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳴人勁極都係羅璇丸同影分身呢兩招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n初代雖然主要玩木遁<br />\n但招數層出不窮 又aoe</blockquote><br />\n鳴人除左影分身同螺旋丸之外<br />\n<br />\n仲有仙人模式、通靈術、組合忍術、尾獸玉、求道玉、蛙組手"},{"pid":"f4110d867603bf2fafd9e4d2144d43124875376a","tid":264422,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你拎個無敵主角同人比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一來年代唔同<br />\n二來你係比緊千手對鳴門+九隻尾獸+先人力量<br />\n<br />\nbtw樓上講得岩 出撚嚟出撚去係螺旋丸</blockquote><br />\n比較就緊係比大家全盛時期啦"},{"pid":"d1266dd59023da6207f323d39e0c18cbd053f08b","tid":264422,"uid":115607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你拎個無敵主角同人比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一來年代唔同<br />\n二來你係比緊千手對鳴門+九隻尾獸+先人力量<br />\n<br />\nbtw樓上講得岩 出撚嚟出撚去係螺旋丸</blockquote><br />\n比較就緊係比大家全盛時期啦</blockquote><br />\n鳴門最有型既造型肯定係打佩恩個時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打完之後已經無用翻個個造型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明咁撚型"},{"pid":"03278361740615b3e737c2a7e535a5ee68c278bc","tid":264422,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:18:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係勁唔過最強嘅三代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n歷代最強火影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e3c3eff21396d7450203f37004e97c31bea7fd","tid":264422,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你拎個無敵主角同人比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一來年代唔同<br />\n二來你係比緊千手對鳴門+九隻尾獸+先人力量<br />\n<br />\nbtw樓上講得岩 出撚嚟出撚去係螺旋丸</blockquote><br />\n比較就緊係比大家全盛時期啦</blockquote><br />\n鳴門最有型既造型肯定係打佩恩個時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打完之後已經無用翻個個造型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明咁撚型</blockquote><br />\n果個造型真係幾正，又似自來也<br />\n<br />\nBtw 六道仙人mode都好型"},{"pid":"bd1bdfa05ce61504fb8c52268140099214ac2562","tid":264422,"uid":61005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:21:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有六道之後唔知點解冇左九尾模式打雷影嗰陣d速度</blockquote><br />\n都唔係太需要啦 求道玉絕對防禦咁濟 加上忍術唔係咁易打得入"},{"pid":"2f0732b60488a37df53b0122490771bebf284726","tid":264422,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:22:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有六道之後唔知點解冇左九尾模式打雷影嗰陣d速度</blockquote><br />\n都唔係太需要啦 求道玉絕對防禦咁濟 加上忍術唔係咁易打得入</blockquote><br />\n去到後期鳴人既瞬身術已經好尾機"},{"pid":"02421c78c0d4685b11b1aed8997b09a42f6c1a06","tid":264422,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人修綀翻黎既力量黎講，我覺得可能初代勁d<br />\n<br />\n陽之力同九隻尾獸既力量我覺得唔應該計落鳴門自己既力量,因為佢唔係長期擁有，佢應該<span style=\"color: red;\">淨係計仙人mode + 九尾mode</span></blockquote><br />\n如果咁既話應該係55波<br />\n<br />\n大家都唔會絕對穩勝"},{"pid":"cec69305172502c63340268bbf363a6fc44fea2f","tid":264422,"uid":22971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:08:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你拎個無敵主角同人比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一來年代唔同<br />\n二來你係比緊千手對鳴門+九隻尾獸+先人力量<br />\n<br />\nbtw樓上講得岩 出撚嚟出撚去係螺旋丸</blockquote><br />\n比較就緊係比大家全盛時期啦</blockquote><br />\n鳴門最有型既造型肯定係打佩恩個時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打完之後已經無用翻個個造型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明咁撚型</blockquote><br />\n果個造型真係幾正，又似自來也<br />\n<br />\nBtw 六道仙人mode都好型</blockquote><br />\n打佩恩時真係最型"},{"pid":"2fdacbdc6e475faf167884391fa299adc62142e6","tid":264422,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:10:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳴人陽之力都收番喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 木遁剋九尾，無陽之力既鳴人同柱間打收硬皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陽之力係純粹用黎封印輝夜<br />\n佢六道型態唔關陽之力事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f9a2fcbd2bf1deacd03baf2fb27d4adf8aabd5","tid":264422,"uid":47866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:53:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都係勁唔過最強嘅三代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n歷代最強火影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n忍術博士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a62adf31cbadb31e5236baca3ad29253251f08","tid":264422,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:53:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鳴人陽之力都收番喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 木遁剋九尾，無陽之力既鳴人同柱間打收硬皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陽之力係純粹用黎封印輝夜<br />\n佢六道型態唔關陽之力事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鳴人最尾同佐助打都無求道玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e7fbbc6e576d2977020eeedb1dab27b1156cec","tid":264422,"uid":51300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:52:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鳴人陽之力都收番喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 木遁剋九尾，無陽之力既鳴人同柱間打收硬皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陽之力係純粹用黎封印輝夜<br />\n佢六道型態唔關陽之力事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n六道型態係因為有齊九隻尾獸的查克拉。"},{"pid":"32db333c933173a37e46630442488f786a02a1b4","tid":264422,"uid":26766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:56:24.000Z","msg":"千手真係型過嗚人好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd8e77408a91220bc671ee563f998cc0cc6cd48","tid":264422,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T11:52:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千手真係型過嗚人好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n六道mode鳴人最型"},{"pid":"c1e141b43f34430465ead0ee0b76bf4b5d3ddfd6","tid":2